<body>

<footer>
```

**Types:** `feat`, `fix`, `docs`, `style`, `refactor`, `test`, `chore`, `ci`, `perf`, `revert`
**Scopes:** `cli`, `templates`, `prompts`, `commands`, `docs`, `deps`, `config`, `readme`

